org.glassfish.tyrus.core.uri

Class Match

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glassfish.tyrus.core.uri.Match

  • public class Match
extends Object
    Defines a match on an endpoint. The match is either exact, or is not exact. If the match is not exact, it means that some of the path segments on the endpoint are variables. In this case, the Match object carries the indices of the variable segments in the endpoint path, the names and the values.
    Author:
    dannycoward
